metadata.title: WALKEE PAWS Stay-On Grippy Socks, All-in-One Dog Anti-Slip Grip, Traction, Protect Floors & Pup's Paws, Easy-On & Off, Stay-On Design, As Seen on Shark Tank, Never Lose a Dog Sock Again (X-Small)
features: PREVENTS SLIPPING AND SLIDING: Comfy, stretchy socks featuring silicon dots for traction and ribbing around the ankle for comfort. Designed to help prevent dogs from slipping on indoor wooden floors and tiles.

EASY ON AND STAYS ON: Thanks to the smart over-the-back design and two convenient adjusters for enhanced fit and comfort, Walkee Paws dog leggings secure snugly over your dog’s back so they stay on. Connectable leggings allow you to take off the back leggings and leave on just the front ones overnight. That way, your pup can rise and shine without slipping on wooden floors!

ALL-DAY WEAR: designed in a 4-way stretch fabric with vents that allow air to circulate so they are super comfy for all-day wear.Plus, they come in a cute unisex bone and paw print that’s aw-dorable on every dog!
PAW-FECT FIT: Adjustable legging straps for height and adjustable back piece for length to ensure the perfect fit on dogs of all shapes and sizes.
EASY TO CLEAN: Walkee Paws dog leggings are conveniently machine washable. Comfortable for Fido, easy on the human too! Bonus - they help protect floors too!
description: Is your pup slipping and sliding on wooden or tile floors? Then help them get a grip with our new Walkee Paws Grippy Socks! Similar in construction to our best-selling Walkee Paws Leggings, Grippy Socks feature silicon grippy socks rather than the classic waterproof rubber boots, and are specifically designed for indoor use. They help protect your floors too... Plus, our Grippy Socks are designed with connectable leggings, allowing you to take off the back leggings and leave on the front socks overnight. That way, your pup can rise and shine without slipping on wooden floors!
